[/color][font=Trebuchet MS][size=3][color=#00ff00]Instructions:[/color][/size][/font]
1-Extract the file and put in data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets
2-Open Skyrim (SKSE) 
3-Load any saved game
4-Open the console and type showracemenu 
5-Select Nord female race and click on "Preset Slot", now press F9 and select my preset.
